    <p class="about-body">I am a person of faith, and that shapes everything — how I treat people, how I handle adversity, and what I stand for. I believe the best salespeople are not the ones who talk the most, they are the ones who listen most deeply and genuinely care about the person across the table.</p>
    <p class="about-body">My summers have taught me as much as my semesters. I have made thousands of cold calls for an independent insurance agency, led a cabin of elementary school kids at a Christian summer camp, and worked in a warehouse. Every experience taught me something about grit, service, and what it means to show up for people.</p>
    <p class="about-body">I chose insurance because I believe in what it does. Protecting people and businesses from risk is meaningful work, and I want to build a career doing it well, with the right values, and for the long haul.</p>
